---
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Home">
	<HeroSection />

	<section class="content-section">
		<div class="content-card">
			<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Developer workspace with laptop and code" />
			<div>
				<h2>Why this demo feels fast</h2>
				<p>
					Each route is intentionally lightweight, giving you a clear way to test navigation and perceived loading speed without distraction. The content stays focused on structure, readability, and visual balance so every transition feels easy to compare.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.content-section {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1.25rem 3rem;
	}

	.content-card {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
	}

	.content-card img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 260px;
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 1rem;
	}

	.content-card h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		color: white;
	}

	.content-card p {
		color: #dbe4ff;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}

	@media (max-width: 760px) {
		.content-card {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
